title: New Creator: CryptoBud
body:
Name: CryptoBud

Socials -
https://www.youtube.com/c/CryptoBud/featured
https://twitter.com/cbudtech

Info - CryptoBud is a crypto enthusiast and content creator. With nearly 80K subscribers, CryptoBud has built a large fan base with his unique insights and opinions on various crypto projects. CryptoBud also is a huge supporter of the Rally project. CryptoBud also tweets additional information and owns a private Discord channel that users can receive exclusive content and information. 

Use Cases -
Coin distribution - YouTube livestream/video launch / Twitter / Discord 
Holding - Exclusive content, Discord roles and channels 
Transacting - Q&As on livestream, Discord admission, course releases

Grant - $1000

A 'yes' approves CryptoBud and a $1000 treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop.
